summary: This isn’t the first time I’ve commented on the subject, but can we just talk about this kind of attitude..?: “I believe that...
body:
This isn’t the first time I’ve commented on the subject, but can we just talk about this kind of attitude..?:

“I believe that she had Drogo kill Viserys.”:

Oh yes, I know. All you anti’s want to believe everything that makes her evil to justify your hate. But it still doesn’t translate to what actually happens on screen. Viserys threatens. Drogo talks. Dany translates. Dany and Drogo look at each other. Khal Drogo gives an order to his men, who take hold of Viserys and then Drogo kills him.

Did Daenerys protest? Did she accept what happened? Sure, man. But can you just acknowledge that he put a sword to her, put a sword to her belly - her child, threatened to abduct her, threatened to cut out her child (which would have killed both her and her child), and reminded us all that he sold her. (and would let thousands of men and horses rape her) But you want to turn this around on Daenerys and bitch about what she did to family?

This fandom is so fucked up in how they try to villainize Daenerys.
